  "text": "It is well known that the hydrogen permeation through the Pd-based membranes follows the so-called \"solution/diffusion\" mechanism, and, in the case of relatively low pressure, its rate-limiting step is assumed to be the diffusion [CITATION_1] . The solution-diffusion mechanism may be expressed by six steps, as reported below:",
